      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metrics with uncertainty bounds must be reported for all QoIs; systematic bias must be characterized and within acceptance limits.",
      "rationale": "Normalized RMS error of 34% for hemolysis index; systematic underprediction at high shear. Uncertainty bounds partially reported. Bias exceeds acceptance limits. Achieved level 2."
