    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for COU2 is formally closed and accepted as a complete assessment record, notwithstanding the finding that the overall regulatory submission decision is Not Accepted. All 13 credibility factors have been evaluated or formally flagged as not-assessed epistemic gaps consistent with MRL 5 requirements. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was performed and is referenced in the assessment narrative. The assessment package is accepted as a valid and complete V&V 40 credibility evidence package documenting the current state of model credibility. Remediation plan required before resubmission.",
